Uses of Interface
print.PrinterI

Packages that use PrinterI
print This package contains classes for Printers. 
print.color This package contains classes for Colored Printers. 
 

Uses of PrinterI in print
 

Classes in print that implement PrinterI
 class Printer
          If you want to create a Printer this is the only class you should use.
 class PrinterTemplate
          This class is a template of a Printer, hence it contains what is common to each Printer implementation offered by the library.
 class TerminalPrinter
          This class is a Terminal implementation of the Printer interface, hence all output is sent to standard output.
 

Uses of PrinterI in print.color
 

Subinterfaces of PrinterI in print.color
 interface ColoredPrinterI
          Every class that implements this interface is called a Colored Printer.
 

Classes in print.color that implement PrinterI
 class ColoredPrinter
          If you want to create a Colored Printer this is the only class you should use.
 class ColoredPrinterNIX
          This class is an implementation of the Colored Printer interface.
 class ColoredPrinterTemplate
          This class is a template of a Colored Printer, hence it contains what is common to each Colored Printer implementation offered by the library.
 class ColoredPrinterWIN
          This class is an implementation of the Colored Printer interface.
